<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Tuscany</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">With sparkling clean streets and gardens, Tuscany real estate also boasts of having one of lowest crime rate in the entire neighborhood.</p>

            <p class="par-xl">A fine combination of suburban tranquility and the modern luxuries of the urban communities.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">Tuscany real estate offers endless opportunities for recreation in the form of swimming, walking trails, fishing and several sporting events including hockey, baseball, softball and even soccer.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">There are over a dozen different subdivisions within Tuscany with housing as diverse as starter homes and condos to glamourous luxury homes with vista views in the North and South. </p>
        </div>
